tweet_text:
What we had to do was:
Instead of installing via command line using wdapp install we were instructed to try installing the MSIXVC via Powershell.
Open PS and navigate to the folder containing your MSIXVC and run the command:
Add-appxpackage .\yourmsixvcfile
